  title         = {First Search for Axion-Like Particles in a Storage Ring Using a Polarized Deuteron Beam},
  author        = {Swathi Karanth and Edward J. Stephenson and Seung Pyo Chang and Volker Hejny and Jörg Pretz and Yannis K. Semertzidis and Andreas Wirzba and Aleksandra Wrońska and Falastine Abusaif and A. Aksentev and Benat Alberdi and Anjali Aggarwal and Achim Andres and Luca Barion and Ilja Bekman and M. Beyss and Christian Böhme and B. Breitkreutz and C. von Byern and Nicola Canale and Guiseppe Ciullo and Sergey Dymov and Nils-Oliver Fröhlich and Ralf Gebel and Kirill Grigoryev and Dieter Grzonka and Jan Hetzel and Otari Javakhishvili and Hoyong Jeong and Andro Kacharava and Vsevolod Kamerdzhiev and Irakli Keshelashvili and A. Kononov and Karim Laihem and Andreas Lehrach and Paolo Lenisa and Nodar Lomidze and Bernd Lorantz and Andrzej Magiera and David Mchedlishvili and Fabian Müller and Alexander Nass and Nikolay N. Nikolaev and Seongtae Park and Andrea Pesce and Vera Ponzca and Dieter Prasuhn and Frank Rathmann and Saad Saddique and Artem Saleev and N. Shurkno and Dito Shergelaskvili and Vera Shmakova and Jamal Slim and Helmut Soltner and Rolf Stassen and Hans Ströher and Mirian Tabidze and Giuseppe Tagliente and Yuri Valdau and Maximilian Vitz and Tim Wagner and Peter Wüstner},
